      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "FDA pump hemolysis benchmark — primary flow regime validation",
      "description": "CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index (RHI) compared against experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark dataset across 5 operating points (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Mean RHI prediction error 8.3%; all 5 operating points satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Turbulence model: SST k-omega with curvature correction.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/pump-hemolysis-uq01",
