      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for computational benchmark validation.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset provides sufficient experimental replicates (n = 3 per operating point) for MRL 2 validation. Formal test sample adequacy assessment not required at this risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance."
    },
