    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate fidelity for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in the Class II CPB device COU. RHI predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points with mean error 8.3%, within the ± 15% acceptance band. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the intended comparative hemolysis assessment.",
